The apparent disagreement between the definitions provided by different authors may reflect different uses of these words in different time periods. It is well-attested that many classifiers underwent frequent changes of meaning throughout history (; ; ), so  p&lt;U+012B&gt; may have had all these meanings at different points in history.↩
